<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">Dear {!Contact.Name},</font><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">I am contacting you to discuss your application for the NASTC fuel card program. As I understand it, &nbsp;you applied for a credit line and for whatever reason was declined .<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">Please understand that there are still several additional methods you have to get the NASTC fuel card with the discounts .<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;">1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Resend the application with another signer.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;">2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Obtain Letter of &nbsp;credit from your bank (sample attached)<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;">3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Do a prepaid account. (call for exact details)<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;">4.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Do a cash Deposit account (call for details)<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;">5.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Contact your NASTC Rep asking concerning their factoring program.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;"><br></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; text-indent: -0.25in;"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If&nbsp;</span>completing<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;a new Electronic&nbsp;</span>Application please do not complete on a cell phone.<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial">All&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 12pt;">o</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">f these methods are</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">good and&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">all&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">will allow you to take advantage of the great savings offered by the good people at NASTC.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">Thank you!!!<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;">John</p></div>]]></td>
